  "message": "\u26a1 Enable React Compiler for automatic memoization (#5049)\n\n- Install babel-plugin-react-compiler and react-compiler-runtime\n- Configure in vite.config.ts via @vitejs/plugin-react babel options\n- Compiler auto-memoizes components and hooks at build time,\n  making most manual useMemo/useCallback calls unnecessary\n\nCloses #5043\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
